  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bc8\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "President Kota thanked US President Biden",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "US President Joe Biden has announced a $ 20 million fund to feed more than 800,000 Sri Lankan children and more than 27,000 pregnant women and nursing mothers.",
        "US President Joe Biden made the remarks while addressing the G7 summit yesterday.",
        "I thank US President Joe Biden for announcing $ 20 million to feed more than 800,000 Sri Lankan children and more than 27,000 pregnant women and nursing mothers. He said the people of Sri Lanka would be grateful for the assistance provided by the United States during this time of crisis."
      ],
